(12, 1, '2017-06-17 19:30:56', '2017-06-17 19:30:56', '<div class="event-page-wrap">\r\n<div class="event-block">\r\n<div class="date-block col-md-1">07/05<span>2017</span></div>\r\n<div class="event-page-cont col-md-10">\r\n<h4>Governing Body Meeting  </h4>\r\n<p>A meeting was held at National Fighway Inspection Bungalow (NH IB), Balasore under the chairmanship of working president of Alumni Society JNV Bagudi, Dr. ParthaSarathi Mishra (1994). Batch representatives from different batches (1994, 1995, 1996, 1997, 2000, 2003, and 2006 of JNVBB) of alumni of JNV Bagudi were present in the meeting. The agenda of the meeting were discussed point wise.</p>\r\n<span class="event-add">NH IB, Balasore. <a hre="#" class="event-map">View map</a></span>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="event-block">\r\n<div class="date-block col-md-1">07/05<span>2017</span></div>\r\n<div class="event-page-cont col-md-10">\r\n<h4>Governing Body Meeting  </h4>\r\n<p>A meeting was held at National Highway Inspection Bungalow (NH IB), Balasore under the chairmanship of working president of Alumni Society JNV Bagudi, Dr. ParthaSarathi Mishra (1994). Batch representatives from different batches (1994, 1995, 1996, 1997, 2000, 2003, and 2006 of JNVBB) of alumni of JNV Bagudi were present in the meeting. The agenda of the meeting were discussed point wise.</p>\r\n<span class="event-add">NH IB, Balasore. <a hre="#" class="event-map">View map</a></span>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Events', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'event', '', '', '2018-06-15 12:44:44', '2018-06-15 12:44:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jnv/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
