(427, 1, '2018-06-12 04:08:14', '2018-06-12 04:08:14', '<strong>Mission </strong>\r\n Constantly strive to build and maintain a strong JNV Bagudi community by being a platform that creates and propagates camaraderie, love and respect. \r\n\r\n Organize events, both on and off the campus, and create other opportunities for the alumni to stay connected with their alma mater. \r\n\r\n Actively manage a corpus fund to help improve infrastructure and other facilities at the institution, and promote meritorious students. \r\n\r\n Foster the Navodayan values such as empathy, discipline, being rooted to ground and the motto \'come to learn, go out to serve\' in the thoughts and deeds of members. \r\n\r\n Channelize the community\'s expertise and resources for generic and specific social causes such as plantation drives, medical camps, clothes distribution and flood relief work. \r\n\r\n Help the community members at times of need through speedy intimation and coordination of decisive action. \r\n\r\n Provide the students of the institution and other community members improved career guidance by tapping into the expertise of senior members. \r\n\r\n<strong>Vision </strong>\r\n Help to make JNV Bagudi one of the best Navodayas in the country by building a strong community of alumni who contribute significantly to their alma mater and the society at large. ', 'Mission & Vision', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mission-vision', '', '', '2018-06-12 04:13:50', '2018-06-12 04:13:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jnv/?page_id=427', 0, 'page', '', 0),
